David Boyer PRINCE, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-350. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 21, 2013. Case below, 524 Fed.Appx. 377 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied. Justice BREYER took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
